Title: Camveda Pure Bhimseni Camphor/Kapoor | 500g
Description:
Camveda Pure Bhimseni Camphor/Kapur is highly effective in medical treatments. It can cure pain, swelling, irritation, anxiety and stress. The natural properties of Camveda Bhimseni Camphor (Kapoor/Kapur) make it suitable for consumption in small quantities by people, except children and pregnant women.
Use: Camphor for medical cure, Camphor for pooja, Camphor for Artis, Camphor for daily use.
